550
00:38:07,015 --> 00:38:09,131
Nevolať? Volať? Nevolať?

551
00:38:09,131 --> 00:38:11,182
Nevolaj, si ako posadnutý stalker.

552
00:38:11,182 --> 00:38:12,948
- Prestaň s tým.
