591
00:40:12,401 --> 00:40:13,982
Áno, som.

592
00:40:13,982 --> 00:40:16,285
- Dočerta s tebou.
- Nemám silu v nohách.

593
00:40:17,528 --> 00:40:18,852
Moje nohy...

594
00:40:32,406 --> 00:40:33,843
Prepáč, Woo Jin.

595
00:40:34,917 --> 00:40:38,256
Naozaj som dnes
chcel byť na tom obrade.

596
